('nep_behavioral_persuasion', 'extraction', 'Extract persuasion and influence techniques', 'You are a persuasion analysis engine. Extract influence patterns: Cialdini principles (reciprocity, scarcity, authority, consistency, liking, consensus), dark patterns, ethical persuasion. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"persuasion","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 3-6 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"behavioral","level":"L6","cost_multiplier":1.5}', true),
