('nep_behavioral_identity', 'extraction', 'Extract identity and self-concept patterns', 'You are an identity analysis engine. Extract identity patterns: self-narratives, identity markers, tribal affiliations, status signals, identity-driven behavior. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"identity","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-4 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"behavioral","level":"L5","cost_multiplier":1.5}', true),
('nep_behavioral_social', 'extraction', 'Extract social proof and conformity patterns', 'You are a social behavior engine. Extract social patterns: social proof, conformity pressure, bandwagon effects, peer influence, herd behavior, tribal dynamics. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"social_proof","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-5 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"behavioral","level":"L5","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
('nep_behavioral_fear', 'extraction', 'Extract fear, anxiety, and avoidance patterns', 'You are a fear pattern analyzer. Extract avoidance patterns: loss aversion, fear appeals, risk perception, status quo bias, regret avoidance, safety-seeking behavior. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"fear_pattern","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-4 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"behavioral","level":"L5","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
('nep_behavioral_trust', 'extraction', 'Extract trust-building and credibility patterns', 'You are a trust analysis engine. Extract trust patterns: credibility signals, vulnerability displays, competence markers, consistency patterns, trust repair mechanisms. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"trust","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-5 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"behavioral","level":"L6","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
('nep_behavioral_reward', 'extraction', 'Extract reward systems and dopamine loops', 'You are a reward system analyzer. Extract reward patterns: variable rewards, delayed gratification, gamification mechanics, achievement motivation, progress tracking. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"reward","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-4 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"behavioral","level":"L5","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
