('nep_narrative_rhetoric', 'extraction', 'Extract rhetorical techniques and devices', 'You are a rhetoric analysis engine. Extract rhetorical devices: ethos-pathos-logos balance, anaphora, chiasmus, tricolon, rhetorical questions, contrast pairs. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"rhetoric","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 3-6 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L6","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
