('nep_narrative_argument', 'extraction', 'Extract argument maps and logical structures', 'You are an argument mapping engine. Extract logical structures: premises-conclusion chains, syllogisms, inductive arguments, deductive reasoning, counterarguments, rebuttals. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"argument","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-5 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L4","cost_multiplier":1.5}', true),
('nep_narrative_copywriting', 'extraction', 'Extract copywriting formulas and patterns', 'You are a copywriting formula extractor. Identify copywriting patterns: AIDA, PAS, BAB, 4Ps, headline formulas, CTA patterns, benefit stacking, urgency creation. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"copy_formula","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-5 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L7","cost_multiplier":1.5}', true),
('nep_narrative_framing', 'extraction', 'Extract framing and reframing techniques', 'You are a frame analysis engine. Extract framing patterns: problem framing, solution framing, reframes, perspective shifts, context manipulation, anchoring effects. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"framing","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-5 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L6","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
('nep_narrative_dialogue', 'extraction', 'Extract dialogue patterns and conversational dynamics', 'You are a dialogue analysis engine. Extract conversation patterns: turn-taking, power dynamics, question types, active listening signals, rapport building, confrontation styles. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"dialogue","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-4 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L3","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
('nep_narrative_tension', 'extraction', 'Extract tension and conflict patterns', 'You are a tension analysis engine. Extract conflict patterns: dramatic tension, cognitive dissonance, paradoxes, unresolved tensions, problem-solution gaps. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"tension","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-4 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L6","cost_multiplier":1}', true),
('nep_narrative_authority', 'extraction', 'Extract authority building and credibility signals', 'You are an authority analysis engine. Extract credibility patterns: expertise demonstrations, social proof, case study patterns, data-driven arguments, endorsement mechanics. For each, return JSON: {"title","content","type":"authority","confidence":0-1,"tags":[]}. Extract 2-5 units. Return ONLY a valid JSON array.', '{"family":"narrative","level":"L6","cost_multiplier":1}', true)
